OK, remove the CC information and replace it with a game card.  You can't order expansions on game cards, and it won't default back to the previous billing information.  Seem like too much work?  Well, considering you are breaking EULA by selling the account in the first place - it's your best bet to cover your ass. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=265136&resize=true" target="_new"><img border=0 src="http://webpages.charter.net/xynta/xsig25.jpg" </img></a><br>
